# English Only in Code and Data

All content inside source files must be written in English:
- variable names, string values, comments, log messages
- seed/fixture data (names, labels, descriptions)
- test data

```js
// ❌ BAD
{ name: 'Молоко 2.5%', brand: 'Простоквашино' }

// ✅ GOOD
{ name: 'Milk 2.5%', brand: 'Prostokvashino' }
```

User-facing UI copy is exempt if the product targets a non-English locale.
